Workflow for generating and optimizing the cavity_depth@node.out file:

1. Run ./python/GenerateCavityFiles.ipynb (Creates file and optimizes horizontal distribution of cavity nodes)
2. Run ./python/SmoothCavityIceBase.ipynb (Smooth the ice base and the seafloor below)
3. Run ./matlab/correct_cavity.m (Adjusts sea floor for numerical stability)
4. Run fesom mesh partitioner
